timeline.bodyText:
I'm assuming HttpServletResponse.SC_OK is typed as int, but this did look strange at first.
Little known Java detail starting in Java 7, you can cast from Object directly to int.  That might make this a bit more clear.
if ( (int)request.getAttribute("dd.http-status") == HttpServletResponse.SC_OK ) { ... }

